--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- T I C K E R   E V E N T
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-- This event will let us know when a turn has been consumed.

Event ticker
  Increase botón:cnt.
  "$pTICK... (turno Nro" say botón:cnt. ")"
  Schedule ticker at hero after 1.
End Event.

